Sundram Fasteners to Boost Wind Energy, Auto-Part Investment, Times Says

-- B y   M a l a v i k a   S h a r m a
-- 
2011-03-18T01:22:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/sundram-fasteners-to-boost-wind-energy-auto-part-investment-times-says.html
  Sundram Fasteners Ltd. (SF) , an Indian
maker of nuts, bolts and fasteners, will increase capital
spending by a third to 2 billion rupees ($44.3 million) in
2011-2012 from this year to develop products for the wind energy
and automotive industries, the Economic Times reported, citing
Chairman Suresh Krishna.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Malavika Sharma in New Delhi at 
 msharma52@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Margo Towie at 
 mtowie@bloomberg.net  